text: <!channel> Does anybody object to me making our Wednesday morning at 10am meeting weekly? If we come upon a Wednesday and we feel that we don’t need it, we can always cancel. But I feel for these first few weeks we will want that time to get things up and running. And that way we have a time and place set aside for us to meet. :partyparrot:  if you’re on board, :sickymouse: if not
I do think every two weeks would work too.
Yeah, it’s super easy/flexible to change the invite but I think at least while we are working out the community agreement and getting our feet wet, we may need a weekly time to meet.
